{"article_id":"eUBd2dJdv7rkRSv1","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump has long promised massive tax cuts .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"|","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Getty Trump :","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"White House will release tax reform plan next week","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"President Donald Trump said Friday","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that the process","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to reform America ' s tax code","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"will kick into high gear next week .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"\" We ' ll be having a big announcement on Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"having to do with tax reform .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"The process has begun long ago ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"but it really formally begins on Wednesday , \"","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Trump said Friday afternoon","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"after signing executive orders at the Treasury Department .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"\" So , \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"he added ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"turning to and pointing at Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"\" go do it . \"","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Earlier on Friday , Trump told The Associated Press","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"that his administration will release its tax reform plan next week - ahead of the White House 's 100-day mark .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"The president provided no details to AP","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"but said","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"individuals and businesses will receive \" massive tax cuts , \"","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"which","depth":16},{"id":24,"text":"he predicted","depth":16},{"id":25,"text":"would be \" bigger","depth":17},{"id":26,"text":"I believe","depth":17},{"id":27,"text":"than any tax cut ever. \"","depth":16},{"id":28,"text":"He added","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"that the plan will be unveiled \" Wednesday or shortly thereafter . \"","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"It ' s the most specific date","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"yet Trump has put on the release of a tax plan .","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"His timing , however , has been off before .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"In February , he said","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"a plan was coming in \" two or three weeks. \"","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"But no plan ever materialized .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"Despite the confidence of the president and his Treasury secretary on Friday ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"a White House official expressed skepticism at Trump ' s self-set deadline","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"to unveil a tax reform plan .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"The tax reform package could come next week -","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"\" or maybe not , \"","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"the official said .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"\" No guarantees . \"","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"House Republicans ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"who have a plan of their own ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"have been eagerly awaiting details on Trump ' s proposal .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Several controversial trial balloons have been floated ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"though it ' s not clear whether they actually came from the White House .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Among them :","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"a carbon tax , a value-added tax and a deep cut to the payroll tax .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"All were considered non-starters on Capitol Hill ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"and the White House knocked down the first two ideas .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Lawmakers will return to Washington next week from their Easter recess","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"facing a deadline","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"to fund the government","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"and a possible floor vote on legislation","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"to repeal","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"and replace Obamacare .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"While the funding deadline was created","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"when Congress passed a continuing resolution","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"to keep the government open last year through April 28 ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"the new emphasis","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"on passing Obamacare repeal","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"seems to be a late push by the White House","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"to have a significant legislative achievement","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"it can tout on Day 100 .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Trump has long promised massive tax cuts","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"but said this week","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"it would be easier to accomplish","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"if Republicans passed legislation","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"to repeal","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"and replace Obamacare first .","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"Health care reform ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"Trump said Tuesday in Wisconsin ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"\" just makes the tax reform easier ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"and it makes it better . \"","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"In his public remarks at the Snap-on facility in Kenosha , Wisconsin , Trump signaled","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"that a tax reform plan would be coming \" very soon . \"","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"\" But health care , we have to get the health care taken care of , \"","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"he said ,","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"adding","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"that the administration would \" march very quickly \"","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"once health care is taken care of .","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"\" You ' re gon na watch .","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"We ' re gon na surprise you .","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"Right , Steve Mnuchin ?","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"Right ? \"","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"Mnuchin once flagged August as a realistic deadline for a tax overhaul","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"but has since acknowledged","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"that is \" highly aggressive to not realistic at this point . \"","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"He also suggested in his interview this week with the Financial Times","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"that the administration has a parallel track","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"that hinges on the success or failure of Obamacare repeal .","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"\" I think","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"as you ' ve heard the president say , even recently ,","depth":16},{"id":95,"text":"he continues to focus on if we can get health care done , \"","depth":16},{"id":96,"text":"Mnuchin said Tuesday .","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"\" And there are a lot of taxes","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"that would be taken care of in Obamacare .","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"I think","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"it ' s fair to say","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"if Obamacare doesn ' t get done ,","depth":17},{"id":102,"text":"and we switch to tax reform ,","depth":17},{"id":103,"text":"there will be some of those taxes","depth":17},{"id":104,"text":"that are taken care of , but most likely not all of the taxes . \"","depth":17},{"id":105,"text":"During the campaign , Trump proposed a top individual tax rate of 33 percent","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"- down from the current 39.6 percent -","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"followed by rates of 25 percent and 12 percent .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"The corporate tax rate would plunge to 15 percent under that plan , down from 35 percent .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Morning Tax","depth":4},{"id":110,"text":"Sign up for our tax policy newsletter","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"and stay informed","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"- weekday mornings , in your inbox .","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"By signing up","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"But Trump has sent mixed signals about a controversial plan","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"to tax imports but not exports , a provision","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"that is crucial to the House Republican plan .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"Whether he embraces it is likely to determine the fate of the idea .","depth":5},{"id":121,"text":"Independent analyses of Trump ' s campaign plan concluded","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"that most of the benefits would flow to wealthy Americans .","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"But Mnuchin has been adamant","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"that the administration ' s final plan would primarily benefit the middle class","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"and that there would be no \" absolute \" cut in taxes for upper-income households .","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"Mnuchin also said","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"that the tax plan would mostly pay for itself through the robust economic growth","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"Trump has said","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"it would unleash .","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"That troubles budget hawks ,","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"who worry","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"the plan could end up adding trillions to the federal debt .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Democrats and transparency advocates have argued","depth":5},{"id":134,"text":"that tax reform is impossible","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"without the president first disclosing his tax returns to the American people","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"to see how he could benefit from legislation","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"he has the authority","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"to sign into law .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"But Trump has not done so ,","depth":5},{"id":140,"text":"and the White House has indicated","depth":6},{"id":141,"text":"that there ' s a chance","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"the president will never disclose his taxes .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":285,"left":146,"right":284,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":0,"right":145,"relation":"attribution","